- Theresa Gionoffrio.

170
00:16:08,780 --> 00:16:10,975
Move on! Move on!

171
00:16:12,580 --> 00:16:15,048
- You knew her?
- Only slightly.

172
00:16:15,140 --> 00:16:18,530
- Come on, Ro, baby. Let's go.
- Oh! Here they come.

173
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:23,458
You folks the Castevets?

174
00:16:23,540 --> 00:16:24,893
We are.

175
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:28,131
You have a Theresa Gionoffrio
living with you?

176
00:16:28,220 --> 00:16:30,529
We do. Has there been an accident?

177
00:16:30,620 --> 00:16:32,895
Brace yourself for some bad news.

178
00:16:32,980 --> 00:16:35,494
She's dead. Jumped out of the window.

179
00:16:35,580 --> 00:16:38,014
That's not possible! It's a mistake!

180
00:16:38,100 --> 00:16:41,729
Artie, you want to let these folks
take a look, please?

181
00:16:43,100 --> 00:16:45,056
I knew this would happen.

182
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:48,849
She got deeply depressed
every three weeks or so.

183
00:16:48,940 --> 00:16:52,091
I told my wife about it,
but she pooh-poohed me.

184
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:54,819
