- Must've been cleaning the windows.
- At midnight?

187
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:06,250
- Why not? Maybe she was!
- Is that her handwriting?

188
00:17:08,220 --> 00:17:10,370
- Yeah.
- Definitely. Absolutely.

189
00:17:10,460 --> 00:17:13,816
I'll see this gets back to you
when we're done.

190
00:17:13,900 --> 00:17:18,018
I don't believe it. I just
don't believe it. She was so happy.

191
00:17:18,100 --> 00:17:22,218
- Who 's the next-of-kin?
- She didn't have anybody, only us.

192
00:17:22,300 --> 00:17:25,133
- She had a brother.
- Did she?

193
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:28,530
- In the navy.
- News to me.

194
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:32,135
- Where is he stationed?
- I don't know.

195
