200
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:48,689
Thank you.

201
00:17:48,780 --> 00:17:51,453
Know anything else
about this brother?

202
00:17:51,540 --> 00:17:54,850
- No, I don't.
- It should be easy to find him.

203
00:17:54,940 --> 00:17:58,410
- I'm so stunned. I'm so sorry.
- It's such a pity.

204
00:17:58,500 --> 00:18:00,331
Well, thank you.

205
00:18:38,780 --> 00:18:43,012
Sometimes I wonder how come
you're the leader of anything.

206
00:18:47,820 --> 00:18:52,416
