02:05:02,090 --> 02:05:04,320
Satan is his father, not Guy.

1412
02:05:04,410 --> 02:05:08,483
He came up from hell
and begat a son of mortal woman.

1413
02:05:08,570 --> 02:05:10,526
- Hail, Satan.
- Hail, Satan.

1414
02:05:10,610 --> 02:05:13,522
Satan is his father,
and his name is Adrian.

1415
02:05:13,610 --> 02:05:18,047
He shall overthrow the mighty
and lay waste their temples.

1416
02:05:18,130 --> 02:05:23,045
He shall wreak vengeance in the name
of the burned and the tortured!

1417
02:05:23,130 --> 02:05:25,644
- Hail, Adrian!
- Hail, Adrian!

1418
02:05:25,730 --> 02:05:27,686
Hail, Satan! Hail, Satan!

1419
02:05:27,770 --> 02:05:29,362
Hail, Satan!

1420
02:05:29,450 --> 02:05:33,648
He chose you. Out of all the women
in the whole world, he chose you.

1421
02:05:33,730 --> 02:05:36,847
He wanted you to be
the mother of his only son.

1422
02:05:36,930 --> 02:05:39,319
His power is stronger than stronger!

1423
02:05:39,410 --> 02:05:42,163
His might shall last
longer than longer!

1424
02:05:42,250 --> 02:05:45,481
- Hail, Satan!
- No!

1425
02:05:46,090 --> 02:05:49,685
It can't be! No!

1426
02:05:49,970 --> 02:05:52,803
- Go look at his hands.
- And his feet.

1427
02:05:54,650 --> 02:05:57,005
Oh, God!

1428
02:05:58,090 --> 02:06:01,685
- God is dead! Satan lives!
- Hail, Satan!

1429
02:06:01,770 --> 02:06:04,330
- The year is one!
- Hail, Satan!

1430
02:06:04,410 --> 02:06:07,482
- The year is one and God is done!
- Oh, God!

1431
02:06:07,570 --> 02:06:11,688
- The year is one!
- Hail, Adrian!

1432
02:06:11,770 --> 02:06:13,920
Hail, Satan!

1433
02:06:14,010 --> 02:06:18,208
Why don't you help us out, Rosemary?
Be a real mother to Adrian.

1434
02:06:18,290 --> 02:06:21,168
You don't have to join
if you don't want to.

1435
02:06:21,250 --> 02:06:23,286
Just be a mother to your baby.

1436
02:06:24,370 --> 02:06:29,125
Minnie and Laura-Louise are too old.
It's not right.

1437
02:06:31,450 --> 02:06:33,202
Think about it, Rosemary.

1438
02:06:45,970 --> 02:06:47,483
Oh, God!

1439
02:06:47,570 --> 02:06:50,687
Oh, shut up or we'll kill you,
milk or no milk.

1440
02:06:50,770 --> 02:06:55,127
You shut up. Rosemary's his mother.
Show some respect.

1441
02:06:57,050 --> 02:07:01,168
Come, my friend.
Come see him. Come see the child.

1442
02:07:10,890 --> 02:07:13,165
What would you like to drink?

1443
02:07:13,930 --> 02:07:18,287
They promised you wouldn't be hurt,
and you haven't been, really.

1444
02:07:18,370 --> 02:07:22,329
I mean, supposing you had the baby
and you lost it.

1445
02:07:23,250 --> 02:07:25,206
Wouldn't that be the same?

1446
02:07:25,290 --> 02:07:28,680
And we're getting
so much in return, Ro.

1447
02:07:38,650 --> 02:07:42,643
Oh, Guy, let me introduce
you to Argyron Stavropoulos.

1448
02:07:42,730 --> 02:07:45,403
How proud you must be.

1449
02:07:45,490 --> 02:07:48,163
Is this the mother?
Why in the name of...

1450
02:07:48,250 --> 02:07:51,720
- Here, drink this.
- What's in it? Tannis root?

1451
02:07:51,810 --> 02:07:55,564
Just plain, ordinary Lipton's tea.
You drink it.

1452
02:08:25,890 --> 02:08:30,441
- Get away from here. Roman!
- You're rocking him too fast.

1453
02:08:30,530 --> 02:08:33,124
Sit down! Put her where she belongs.

1454
02:08:33,210 --> 02:08:36,759
You're rocking him too fast.
That's why he's crying.

1455
02:08:36,850 --> 02:08:40,160
- Mind your own business.
- Let Rosemary rock him.

1456
02:08:40,250 --> 02:08:43,083
- Sit with the others.
- She's liable to...

1457
02:08:43,170 --> 02:08:45,889
Sit down with the others,
Laura-Louise.

1458
02:08:54,610 --> 02:08:56,566
Rock him.

1459
02:08:58,530 --> 02:09:01,806
You're trying to get me
to be his mother.

1460
02:09:01,890 --> 02:09:03,801
Aren't you his mother?

